u-Ti%E1%BB%81u-%E1%BA%A8n/poem-gtkkCY-irvw6H6NKdG76_w">Tặng Chu Tiều Ẩn - 贈朱樵隱</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/T%C3%A2y-S%C6%A1n-thi-ho%E1%BA%A1-gi%E1%BA%A3-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-d%C6%B0-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1i-d%E1%BB%A5ng-ti%E1%BB%81n-v%E1%BA%ADn-vi-t%E1%BA%A1/poem-sTETKXl0tUNMHQSfVPqeGQ">Tây Sơn thi hoạ giả tam thập dư nhân, tái dụng tiền vận vi tạ - 西山詩和者三十餘人，再用前韻為謝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-T%E1%BB%99/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-Bi-s%C6%A1n-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-U2j77u_4FSOTrAmlcwXmCw">Thạch Bi sơn ngẫu thành - 石碑山偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-T%E1%BB%99/author-MWJzut9wDqpdBdTOmcwp0g">Nguyễn Trường Tộ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-t%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1DEtLwJiIIKkCpcoJKSFdw">Thu tận - 秋盡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Tr%C3%B9ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-HJgsG010h4fvuLJEYOClMw">Trùng tặng kỳ 1 - 重贈其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
